(75268, 237407, 6805, 1, 'All In', '★全球1500萬張專輯/單曲銷量，橫跨流行/搖滾/成人抒情領域的美派Post-Grunge團隊★\r\n★首度以四人組合現身，有請合作過三張專輯的Jude Cole(Jewel、Beth Orton)再次操刀★\r\n★情歌王子Richard Marx量身訂作的“Had Enough”，邀來American Idol歌唱比賽選手Chris Daughtry共同打造；與創作天才Kevin Rudolf合力譜寫首波主打“Halfway Gone”★\r\n\r\n頂著全球1500萬張專輯+單曲銷售量，橫跨流行、搖滾、成人抒情領域，秉持美派Post-Grunge風格，用歌聲唱出生命、愛與成長，讓文字歌詠愛戀、讚嘆人生、珍藏回憶，這都是Lifehouse/生命之屋合唱團最真情的動人告白。一鳴驚人的“Hanging By A Moment”徘徊告示牌55週的紀錄，直接進入Billboard的「史上最成功搖滾歌曲」第25名+「2000-2009年間最佳單曲」第26名，自此開始記載Lifehouse未來10年的風光歌唱生涯。\r\n\r\n被稱為天才型創作家的Jason Wade，擔綱Lifehouse的主唱/吉他手和創作主腦，15歲認識了可從鍵盤、長號、長笛、鼓一路玩到貝斯的音樂神童Sergio Andrade，都是Lifehouse團員裡最受矚目的焦點。1999年底推出首張專輯『No Name Face』，僅在美國地區的銷售量即突破兩百萬門檻。2002年再接再厲發行『Stanley Climbfall』，亮出全球兩百萬張紀錄。第三張同名大碟『Lifehouse』發行前，貝斯手Sergio離團，換上Bryce Soderberg入替，仍拿下白金唱片認證。2007年延續一貫流暢風格的『Who We Are』，再次風光稱霸英國金榜冠軍。\r\n\r\n正式踏入歌壇第十年的Lifehouse，讓演唱會的客席樂手Ben Carey加入，首度以四人組合現身問世全新大碟【Smoke &amp; Mirrors】，有請合作過3張專輯的Jude Cole(Jewel、Beth Orton)再次操刀。以順暢吉他敲起“All In”序幕，不失搖滾力道的衝擊出過癮聲線；由情歌王子Richard Marx量身訂作的“Had Enough”，邀來American Idol歌唱比賽中，首位雙霸告示牌流行+搖滾榜冠軍的選手Chris Daughtry，共同用最熾熱的柔情打造優質極品；讓黑人嘻哈區塊失守的白人天才Kevin Rudolf合力譜寫首波主打“Halfway Gone”，毫無顧忌的高聲唱出搖滾悍勁，釋放出無比能量，不僅掀起流行市場騷動，混音版本更打入舞曲點播榜內；一首對於年輕人安全駕駛的關懷之歌“From Where You Are”，同時也紀念Jason年僅16歲因車禍過世的朋友，已率先攻上數位榜Top15；特別重新詮釋2000年舊作“Everything”，描述對信仰的忠誠，更為抒情的線條，至後段逐漸攀升的音場，輕易牽引出聆聽者內心激昂情緒。', '2010-03-19 00:00:00', 2010, 19, 0, 7, '', 'All night staring at the ceiling\ncounting for minutes I''ve been feeling this way\nSo far away and so alone\n\nBut you know it''s alright\nI came to my senses\nLetting go of my defenses\nThere''s no way I''m giving up this time\nYeah, you know I''m right here\nI''m not losing you this time\n\nAnd I''m all in, nothing left to hide\nI''ve fallen harder than a landslide\nI spent a week away from you last night\nAnd now I''m calling, calling out your name\nEven if I lose the game, I''m all in\nI''m all in tonight, yeah I''m all in, I''m all in for life\n\nThere''s no taking back\nwhat we''ve got''s too strong,\nwe''ve had each other''s back for too long\nThere''s no breaking up this time\nAnd you know it''s okay, I came to my senses\nLetting go of my defenses\nThere''s no way I''m giving up this time\n\nAnd I''m all in, nothing left to hide\nI''ve fallen harder than a landslide\nI spent a week away from you last night\nAnd now I''m calling, calling out your name\nEven if I lose the game, I''m all in\nI''m all in tonight, yeah I''m all in, I''m all in for life\n\nI want it, I want it, I want it\nI want it, I want it, I want it, yeah\nI want it, I want it, I want it, yeah\n\nAnd I''m all in, calling out your name\nEven if I lose the game, I''m all in, I''m all in for life\nAnd I''m all in, nothing left to hide\nI''ve fallen harder than a landslide\nI spent a week away from you last night\nAnd now I''m calling, calling out your name\nEven if I lose the game, I''m all in\nI''m all in tonight, yeah I''m all in, I''m all in for life\nYeah I''m all in, I''m all in for life', 236, '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-05-06 15:29:27', '2015-03-12 14:06:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
